<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>واشترطها للإمام الشِّيعةُ الإمامية <span class="c2">(٩)</span> ..........................................................................<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
